The paper deals with the problem of Multi-Lingual Scene Text (MLT) detection and recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of a large scale synthetic dataset to assist training, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) or machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper presents a baseline End-to-End recognition method, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
